# YouTube Data API v3 key (server-side only — TICKET-8 in-app search).
# Leave empty for local dev / CI: the app builds and runs in degraded mode
# (free-text search shows the fallback copy; paste-a-YouTube-link still works).
# Provision in Google Cloud (enable "YouTube Data API v3", create an API key,
# restrict to that API + your server referrers) and set it in Vercel env + local .env.
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=
